Locale.Value:
Fixes and Improvements in 2.16.5
- Fixed a crash at launch on Windows 32-bit (7, 8 and 10)
- Photos: when a Live Photo is not stored locally, it is now also possible to download the Live Photos video asset from iCloud
- Photos: when a photo cannot be found on iCloud, the Apple to all checkbox to skip the missing item now works as expected
- Photos: fixed a rare crash "PhotoIconConverter.Convert - System.ComponentModel.Win32Exception" while browsing (Windows)
- Device Advanced Info: added Developer Mode Enabled
- Music: when sotring tracks by Album Mame, the tracks are not also sorted by Disk Number and Track Number
- Music: AIFF (.aif) files can now be transfered to the device from the Music section (Windows)
- In-App Store: the 3-D Secure verification window is now displayed properly and purchasing through PayPal also works as expected
